*Oboje* su znali da će kraj biti tužan. (Both of them knew that the ending would be sad.)

*Oboje* su se složili oko odluke. (Both of them agreed on the decision.)

Oni *oboje* vole da se šale. (Both of them like to joke.)

*Obojica* su studirali medicinu. (Both of them studied medicine.)

*Oboju* je bilo žao što se to desilo. (Both of them were sorry that it happened.)

*Obojici* je trebalo da se spreme. (Both of them had to get ready.)